'''Pavillion''' was an underwater [[City/Legends|city]] on [[Iskalon/Legends|Iskalon]]. It was built so [[Iskalonian|water]] and air breathing visitors could interact with each other. However, Pavillion was destroyed in [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]] when the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] set off the [[Iskalon Effect]], a huge tidal wave which was meant to kill [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] during his visit to Iskalon.

